quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,Chisimu ŵakun'jogopa (Allah) chachiŵa m’miulili (jakusisimila chenene) ni achitutumule
  77,42,Ni isogosi yatachiilaluchilaga
  77,43,"(Tachasalila kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mwakusengwa ligongo lya ayila (yambone) yamwaliji nkutenda.”"
  77,44,Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  77,45,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,46,"(E, jenumanja achimakafili!) Lyagani ni kusengwa panandi (mukandaŵi kannono kaumi wa duniyau), chisimu ŵanganyammwe ŵaleŵeleŵe"
  77,47,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,48,"Soni pati iŵechetedwe kukwao (yanti): “Jinamani (kuswali).” Ngakwinamaga"
  77,49,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,50,Ana ni abalichi jatachijikulupilila panyuma pa aji (Qur’an)